### Checklist for Lifecycle Integration

When implementing ANY list or detail view with VerifiableModel:

- [ ] Add lifecycle fields to TypeScript interface
- [ ] Include LifecycleBadges in detail view header
- [ ] Include LifecycleBadgeCompact in list view
- [ ] Add LifecycleActions to detail view (if user has permissions)
- [ ] Add LifecycleHistory button/modal
- [ ] Add lifecycle status filter to list view
- [ ] Disable edit when status != OPEN
- [ ] Show helpful message when locked
- [ ] Refresh data after lifecycle action (router.refresh())
- [ ] Handle mobile responsive layout

